snippet.title: CarboRaider High-Carb Rush
snippet.description:
Carb the Fruit up, and get into high-gear.  Get a RUSH out of life, with music and a fruit-based diet.
Powerful Info and Awesome Music.  Escape the Youtube Diet Matrix with a smart skeptic who actually KNOWS what he's talking about, with 26 years experience as a vegan, and 53 years living WHILE paying attention.

Check out this Master who keeps it REAL ... real logic, delivered with comedy(when applicable), showing the flawed thinking about health, and what's REALLY GOING ON.
